OL,3,CMan mixed sperm with father's to get
OL,4,Cpartner pregnant
OL,6,FA man who mixed his sperm with his
OL,7,Ffather's to help his partner get
OL,8,Fpregnant will not have to have a
OL,9,Fpaternity test, the High Court has
OL,10,Fruled.
OL,12,FAfter experiencing fertility problems
OL,13,Fand being unable to afford IVF
OL,14,Ftreatment, the Barnsley man, known as
OL,15,FPQ, and his then-partner, JK, agreed
OL,16,Fto mix his sperm with his father's,
OL,17,FRS, and inject it into the woman, the
OL,18,Fcourt heard at a hearing last month.
