OL,6,FBut in a judgment on Thursday, Justice
OL,7,FPoole dismissed the bid, finding the
OL,8,Fcouncil had "no stake in the outcome".
OL,10,FThe judge said the family had "created
OL,11,Fa welfare minefield", adding: "I
OL,12,Fcannot believe that JK, PQ and RS
OL,13,Fproperly thought through the
OL,14,Framifications of their scheme for JK
OL,15,Fto become pregnant, otherwise it is
OL,16,Funlikely that they would have embarked
OL,17,Fupon it.
