OL,6,F"It must be acknowledged that the
OL,7,Fcircumstances of D's conception cannot
OL,8,Fnow be undone," he said.
OL,10,F"Without testing, his biological
OL,11,Fpaternity remains uncertain but there
OL,12,Fis a strong chance, to say the least,
OL,13,Fthat the person he thinks is his
OL,14,Fgrandfather is his biological father,
OL,15,Fand that the person he thinks is his
OL,16,Ffather is his biological half-brother."
