OL,6,FDismissing the council's bid, the
OL,7,Fjudge said the body does not have
OL,8,Fparental responsibility or a "personal
OL,9,Finterest" in the boy's biological
OL,10,Fparentage.
OL,12,F"It may wish to know who is D's
OL,13,Fbiological father, but it has no stake
OL,14,Fin the outcome of its application,"
OL,15,Fsaid Justice Poole.
OL,17,F"A wish to uphold the public interest
OL,18,Fin maintaining accurate records of
OL,19,Fbirths does not confer a personal
OL,20,Finterest in the determination of such
OL,21,Fan application."
